Our Team



Careers at William Lyon Homes
At William Lyon Homes we believe that a great company, just like a beautiful home, starts with a solid foundation. Our foundation is our employees, and we are committed to hiring and retaining top talent.
We promote a company culture that fosters innovation, collaboration, and creative solutions to an ever-challenging and changing market environment. Our team is made up of experienced, loyal employees, many of whom have been with the company more than 20 years. We value a diverse workplace, and offer our employees exciting career opportunities from construction and sales to marketing and finance. At William Lyon Homes, your individual talents are cultivated in a dynamic team environment where you can personally and professionally thrive.
 






