William Lyon Homes




William Lyon Homes Celebrates its 60th Anniversary and an Enduring Legacy of Pride and Integrity.
William Lyon Homes is committed to building neighborhoods that stand the test of time and to delivering brand new homes of uncompromising quality. Our 60th anniversary marks an extraordinary milestone and is a testament to our team’s loyalty and dependability, dedication to customer service and passion for homebuilding that is evident in every new home we build.
From innovative townhome designs to luxury residences, we create opportunities in the finest locations to elevate the way you want to live. William Lyon Homes is well-established in California, Nevada, Arizona and Colorado and proudly continues to expand our brand with Polygon Northwest Homes, our division in Washington and Oregon.











              Customer Satisfaction is our Priority  Every Step of the Way              

William Lyon Homes and Polygon Homes were recognized at the Eliant 2017 Homebuyers Choice Awards!
