William Lyon Homes Selling Brand New Homes in the Greater Las Vegas Area
William Lyon Homes Offers Beautiful New Homes in Greater Las Vegas and Mountain Falls 
From the deep natural hues of the Red Rock Mountains to the resort-style luxury of Lake Las Vegas to championship golf courses and the bright lights of The Strip, the Las Vegas Valley offers something for everyone’s hopes and dreams. If your idea of a perfect day is playing 18 holes of golf, shopping at upscale boutiques or enjoying an award-winning show, this region is brimming with promise and possibility.
 



