New Homes in Arizona by William Lyon Homes
William Lyon Homes Offers a Wide Array of New Home Choices in the Phoenix Metro Area 
Gorgeous desert landscapes and sunny days make the Phoenix metropolitan area a homebuyer favorite for its mild climate and leisure destinations. The Grand Canyon National Park, one of the world's premier natural attractions boasts the most breathtaking views in the state, while dramatic mountain ranges and lush golf courses dot the landscape of this beautifully vibrant region.



