New Homes in Colorado by William Lyon Homes
William Lyon Homes Offers a Wide Array of Brand New Home Choices in Northern Colorado and the Denver Metro Area
From the majestic snow-capped peaks of Rocky Mountain National Park to the dynamic cultural environment of Denver, the Mile High City, Colorado has endless options to delight outdoor enthusiasts and urban dwellers alike. With world-class ski resorts for winter activities, miles of hiking and biking trails for summer fun, plus Denver’s award-winning dining and seven professionals sports teams, residents enjoy a multitude of opportunities for leisure and recreation in naturally breathtaking surroundings.



