William Lyon-A Up 28.8% Since SmarTrend Uptrend Call (WLH)



Written on Fri, 07/21/2017 - 1:13am
 By Nick Russo
SmarTrend identified an Uptrend for William Lyon-A (NYSE:WLH) on January 26th, 2017 at $18.14.  In approximately 6 months, William Lyon-A has returned 28.81% as of today's recent price of $23.36.In the past 52 weeks, William Lyon-A share prices have been bracketed by a low of $14.13 and a high of $24.51 and are now at $23.36, 65% above that low price.  Over the past week, the 200-day moving average (MA) has gone down 1.3% while the 50-day MA has advanced 2.5%.William Lyon Homes provides construction services. The Company designs and constructs residential properties. William Lyon Homes serves customers throughout the United States.SmarTrend will continue to scan these moving averages and a number of other proprietary indicators for any shifts in the trajectory of William Lyon-A shares.Log in and add William Lyon-A (WLH) to your watchlist today so you can receive a real-time alert when the shares are about to change trend.



