William Lyon Homes





The Grand Collection at Sterling RidgeLas Vegas, NevadaGreater Las Vegas


New Luxury Homes at The Ridges in Summerlin from the Low $900,000s
Brilliant, contemporary architecture underscores the beauty of The Grand Collection at Sterling Ridge at The Ridges in Summerlin. The neighborhood’s sleek, contemporary styling seamlessly blends with desert surroundings and luxury designs surrounded by guard-gated privacy feature indoor/outdoor living spaces of distinction. Voluminous interior spaces accentuate the homes’ expansive views and natural light.
The Grand Collection at Sterling Ridge presents two-story designs that range from approximately 3,546 to 4,180 square feet, with up to 4 bedrooms, 4.5 baths and a host of upgrade-quality standard features and personalizing opportunities. Courtyards and elegant foyers lead to inspired Great Rooms, dining areas and gourmet kitchens stunningly appointed with granite countertops and high-end Bosch appliances and Kohler® fixtures. Additional highlights include a 3-car tandem garage or garage bays, with covered verandas, interior courtyards and decks available per plan.
 



